author: Written by: FOX8Live.com Staff
title: Saints Power Rankings: What the national media are saying
text:
NEW ORLEANS (WVUE) - "Can they rebound from blowout at Philly?"
That's the question on sports writers' minds as the Saints get ready to take on their rival (and undefeated) Atlanta Falcons.
After a blow-out loss to the Philadelphia Eagles on Sunday, sports writers across the country panned the Saints, dropping them into the bottom 10 of their weekly rankings almost universally.
Click through the slideshow to see their critiques, and solutions, as the Saints look to bounce back.
